<p class="note-body">This section is referred to in <uscode edition="1994" range="77b, 77d, 77l, 77q, 77ddd, 80a-3, 80a-24" section="77b" title="15">sections 77b, 77d, 77l, 77q, 77ddd, 80a–3, 80a–24 of this title</uscode>; title 11 section 101; title 12 sections 1813, 2279aa–12, 2290; title 22 sections 282k, 283h, 283ii, 285h, 286k–1, 290i–9, 290l–7, 290m; title 25 section 646; title 49 section 11367.</p>
