ine';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="477">Pub. L. 96–477,</plaw> title VII, §702, <statuteatlarge page="2295" volume="94">94 Stat. 2295</statuteatlarge></a>; Oct. 13, 1982, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=96&amp;page=1409" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="97" isprivate="false" number="303">Pub. L. 97–303,</plaw> §2, <statuteatlarge page="1409" volume="96">96 Stat. 1409</statuteatlarge></a>; Aug. 10, 1984, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=98&amp;page=1265" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="98" isprivate="false" number="376">Pub. L. 98–376,</plaw> §6(a), <statuteatlarge page="1265" volume="98">98 Stat. 1265</statuteatlarge></a>; Oct. 3, 1984, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=98&amp;page=1689" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="98" isprivate="false" number="440">Pub. L. 98–440,</plaw> title I, §101, <statuteatlarge page="1689" volume="98">98 Stat. 1689</statuteatlarge></a>; Oct. 22, 1986, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=100&amp;page=2095" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="514">Pub. L. 99–514,</plaw> §2, <statuteatlarge page="2095" volume="100">100 Stat. 2095</statuteatlarge></a>; Oct. 28, 1986, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=100&amp;page=3214" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="571">Pub. L. 99–571,</plaw> title I, §102(a)–(d), <statuteatlarge page="3214-3216" pages="3214-3216" volume="100">100 Stat. 3214–3216</statuteatlarge></a>; Dec. 4, 1987, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=101&amp;page=1253" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="181">Pub. L. 100–181,</plaw> title III, §§301–306, <statuteatlarge page="1253" volume="101">101 Stat. 1253</statuteatlarge></a>, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=101&amp;page=1254" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank">1254</a>; Nov. 19, 1988, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=102&amp;page=4681" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="704">Pub. L. 100–704,</plaw> §6(a), <statuteatlarge page="4681" volume="102">102 Stat. 4681</statuteatlarge></a>; Aug. 9, 1989, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=103&amp;page=441" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="101" isprivate="false" number="73">Pub. L. 101–73,</plaw> title VII, §744(u)(1), <statuteatlarge page="441" volume="103">103 Stat. 441</statuteatlarge></a>; Oct. 15, 1990, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=104&amp;page=952" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="101" isprivate="false" number="429">Pub. L. 101–429,</plaw> title V, §503, <statuteatlarge page="952" volume="104">104 Stat. 952</statuteatlarge></a>; Nov. 15, 1990, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=104&amp;page=2717" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="101" isprivate="false" number="550">Pub. L. 101–550,</plaw> title II, §§203(b), 204, <statuteatlarge page="2717" volume="104">104 Stat. 2717</statuteatlarge></a>, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=104&amp;page=2718" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank">2718</a>; Dec. 17, 1993, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=107&amp;page=2350" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="103" isprivate="false" number="202">Pub. L. 103–202,</plaw> title I, §§106(b)(2)(A), 109(a), <statuteatlarge page="2350" volume="107">107 Stat. 2350</statuteatlarge></a>, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=107&amp;page=2352" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank">2352</a>; Sept. 23, 1994, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=108&amp;page=2198" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank"><plaw congress="103" isprivate="false" number="325">Pub. L. 103–325,</plaw> title II, §202, title III, §347(a), <statuteatlarge page="2198" volume="108">108 Stat. 2198</statuteatlarge></a>, <a href="/statviewer.htm?volume=108&amp;page=2241" onmouseout="this.style.textDecoration='none';" onmouseover="this.style.textDecoration='underline';" style="text-decoration: none;color: #0F0D61;" target="_blank">2241</a>.)</p>
<!-- field-end:sourcecredit -->
