<p class="note-body">Subsec. (b)(6). <plaw congress="88" isprivate="false" number="467">Pub. L. 88–467,</plaw> §6(b), designated second through fifth sentences of fourth par. as (6) and, in provision constituting first sentence of par. (6) substituted "any registration under this subsection" for "any such registration" and inserted "(which may consist solely of affidavits and oral argument)" after "opportunity for hearing".</p>
